279
00:11:39.780 --> 00:11:42.660
The word here recount literally means to count.

280
00:11:42.660 --> 00:11:45.340
Like it's like one, two, three, four.

281
00:11:45.380 --> 00:11:46.940
Let me think of George Mueller.

282
00:11:46.940 --> 00:11:48.300
Do you know him?

283
00:11:48.300 --> 00:11:52.260
In the 19th century, he cared for orphans specifically.

284
00:11:52.260 --> 00:11:55.740
