287
00:12:00.620 --> 00:12:02.500
all of his prayer requests.

288
00:12:02.500 --> 00:12:04.900
And it's said for people who've studied his journals

289
00:12:04.900 --> 00:12:06.380
and that kind of thing that over time,

290
00:12:06.380 --> 00:12:08.380
you can go back and see that there were over

291
00:12:08.380 --> 00:12:12.900
50,000 specific answers to prayer.

292
00:12:12.900 --> 00:12:14.580
So he would write every single day,

293
00:12:14.580 --> 00:12:15.420
all these different things.

294
00:12:15.420 --> 00:12:17.380
And when the Lord would answer the prayer,

295
00:12:17.380 --> 00:12:19.980
