296
00:12:19.980 --> 00:12:22.540
So he could literally go back and count.

297
00:12:22.540 --> 00:12:24.300
So Lord, you've done this, you've done this,

298
00:12:24.300 --> 00:12:26.580
you've done this, and he's praising the Lord

299
00:12:26.580 --> 00:12:28.940
for those things.

300
00:12:29.940 --> 00:12:32.260
So whether or not we keep a prayer journal in that way,

301
00:12:32.260 --> 00:12:33.500
we should be able to look back and say,

302
00:12:33.500 --> 00:12:34.740
here's what the Lord has done,

303
00:12:34.740 --> 00:12:36.740
and we praise him for that.

304
00:12:36.740 --> 00:12:38.460
But you know this recounting is also part

305
00:12:38.460 --> 00:12:41.140
