306
00:12:41.140 --> 00:12:43.700
So in verse 11, we saw a moment ago

307
00:12:43.700 --> 00:12:46.140
as we sing praises, he also says,

308
00:12:46.140 --> 00:12:48.980
tell among the peoples his deeds.

309
00:12:48.980 --> 00:12:52.240
So tell it out, not just to yourself,

310
00:12:52.240 --> 00:12:54.340
and not just to one another,

311
00:12:54.340 --> 00:12:57.940
but in a way that's public to the world around you.

312
00:12:59.380 --> 00:13:02.180
So praising God isn't just something that we do in private,

313
00:13:02.180 --> 00:13:05.100
it's how we bear witness to the glory of God

314
00:13:05.100 --> 00:13:07.180
in the world.

315
00:13:07.180 --> 00:13:09.860
The Lord has made us for praise,

316
00:13:09.860 --> 00:13:12.580
and he's glorified in all the earth

317
00:13:12.580 --> 00:13:16.540
as his people praise him among the nations.

