00:13:22.300 --> 00:13:26.020
It says that they were telling the mighty works of God

321
00:13:26.020 --> 00:13:27.460
in the things that they were saying.

322
00:13:27.460 --> 00:13:31.820
So they went out speaking about God's wonderful deeds.

323
00:13:31.820 --> 00:13:33.840
Just let me see here in verse one.

324
00:13:34.740 --> 00:13:37.380
So there's recounting, but there's also singing.

325
00:13:37.380 --> 00:13:40.300
I won't say much about this, but it's certainly here.

326
00:13:40.300 --> 00:13:42.380
I will sing praise to your name.

327
00:13:42.380 --> 00:13:45.820
We're commanded, sing praises to the Lord.

328
00:13:45.820 --> 00:13:48.540
So praise finds expression not only in what we say,

329
00:13:48.540 --> 00:13:50.460
