376
00:15:47.380 --> 00:15:50.700
In vain do they worship me teaching commandments

377
00:15:50.700 --> 00:15:55.700
or teaching us commandments, the traditions of men.

378
00:15:56.260 --> 00:15:58.260
So true praise isn't performative.

379
00:15:59.860 --> 00:16:01.660
Here there is no division between

380
00:16:01.660 --> 00:16:04.220
what David's saying on the outside

381
00:16:04.220 --> 00:16:07.420
