00:16:12.540 --> 00:16:14.380
So he says, I will give thanks, yes?

385
00:16:14.380 --> 00:16:16.620
But let's go back to that verse, give thanks how?

386
00:16:16.620 --> 00:16:19.100
With my whole heart.

387
00:16:20.460 --> 00:16:23.700
So he's truly aware and deeply appreciative

388
00:16:23.700 --> 00:16:26.380
of God's grace, not just kind of saying thank you.

389
00:16:26.380 --> 00:16:28.820
You know, we've always kind of told the kids

390
00:16:28.820 --> 00:16:31.380
