391
00:16:32.500 --> 00:16:37.260
There was one time when a lady from our,

392
00:16:37.260 --> 00:16:40.660
an older lady from our church came to our house

393
00:16:40.660 --> 00:16:43.340
with a present for one of our children.

394
00:16:43.340 --> 00:16:46.780
And I won't tell you which one of our children it was,

395
00:16:46.780 --> 00:16:50.180
but when the lady gave this gift to her,

396
00:16:52.300 --> 00:16:57.300
she said, thank you, why are your teeth yellow?

397
00:16:58.140 --> 00:17:03.140
So she was saying thank you, the expression was there,

398
00:17:05.140 --> 00:17:07.540
but her mind was in a completely different place

399
00:17:07.540 --> 00:17:10.220
focusing in on those teeth.

400
00:17:10.220 --> 00:17:11.580
Anyway, back to what we were saying.

401
00:17:11.580 --> 00:17:15.500
Yeah, so true Thanksgiving involves our minds and hearts,

402
00:17:15.500 --> 00:17:17.580
not just our words.

403
00:17:18.620 --> 00:17:20.140
Where else do we see it?

404
00:17:20.140 --> 00:17:24.860
Verse two, I will be glad and exalts in you.

