418
00:18:10.880 --> 00:18:14.360
That's what the word means to leap, to jump for joy.

419
00:18:14.360 --> 00:18:16.800
So we're leaping in triumph.

420
00:18:16.800 --> 00:18:18.600
And that leads to why we praise God.

421
00:18:18.600 --> 00:18:20.960
Okay, so we've seen how do we praise God?

422
00:18:20.960 --> 00:18:22.560
We praise God with integrity.

423
00:18:22.560 --> 00:18:24.840
So there's that external thing that's flowing from a heart

424
00:18:24.840 --> 00:18:26.520
that's after him, rejoicing in him.

425
00:18:27.560 --> 00:18:29.680
And why did we praise God?

426
00:18:29.680 --> 00:18:34.680
Okay, we praise God because of who he is and what he does.

427
00:18:35.800 --> 00:18:38.240
So we praise God because he is worthy

428
00:18:38.240 --> 00:18:40.540
because he does wondrous things.

429
00:18:42.200 --> 00:18:44.000
Or we can praise God for many things.

430
00:18:44.000 --> 00:18:45.560
But here in this Psalm specifically,

431
00:18:45.560 --> 00:18:48.680
he's being praised as the God who is highly exalted

432
00:18:48.680 --> 00:18:51.880
and triumphs over all of his enemies.

433
00:18:51.880 --> 00:18:54.920
What I wanna do is just to split that into three truths

434
00:18:54.920 --> 00:18:57.120
about God that we see in the Psalm.

435
00:18:57.120 --> 00:19:00.120
Like he's praising this God who's exalted above all

436
00:19:00.120 --> 00:19:01.160
and triumphs over his enemies.

437
00:19:01.160 --> 00:19:02.640
But let's break that into three, okay?

438
00:19:02.640 --> 00:19:04.400
So he's praising God first of all

439
00:19:04.400 --> 00:19:07.600
because God is supreme.

440
00:19:07.600 --> 00:19:08.600
Why do we praise God?

441
00:19:08.600 --> 00:19:10.960
We praise him because of his supremacy.

442
00:19:11.880 --> 00:19:13.160
So the end of verse two.

443
00:19:13.160 --> 00:19:15.040
I will sing praise to your name.

444
00:19:15.040 --> 00:19:18.040
Oh, most high.

445
00:19:19.160 --> 00:19:21.840
So one of the ways that God reveals himself in scripture

446
00:19:21.840 --> 00:19:24.880
is by the names that he reveals himself by.

447
00:19:24.880 --> 00:19:26.880
So you have a lot of them to start with L.

