00:20:07.600 --> 00:20:11.320
So from God's throne, he is reigning in righteousness

462
00:20:11.320 --> 00:20:13.520
and executing justice.

463
00:20:13.520 --> 00:20:15.320
And his reign will never end.

464
00:20:15.320 --> 00:20:16.960
So you see that in verse seven.

465
00:20:16.960 --> 00:20:18.720
The Lord sits enthroned forever.

466
00:20:18.720 --> 00:20:21.520
He has established his throne for justice

