498
00:21:58.360 --> 00:22:01.440
Like cities come and cities go.

499
00:22:02.440 --> 00:22:06.880
Empires rise and empires fall.

500
00:22:07.840 --> 00:22:11.720
But the Lord who is on high, seated upon his throne,

501
00:22:11.720 --> 00:22:14.160
