00:35:02.880 --> 00:35:04.200
We're not gonna spend a lot of time here

811
00:35:04.200 --> 00:35:05.880
but I just wanna read this as we close

812
00:35:05.880 --> 00:35:07.840
because I've just been amazed

813
00:35:07.920 --> 00:35:11.120
at the way that Hebrews 13 ties together

814
00:35:11.120 --> 00:35:12.440
so many of these things

815
00:35:12.440 --> 00:35:15.240
and calls us to the same kind of praise.

816
00:35:20.280 --> 00:35:24.480
Verse 12 says that Jesus suffered outside the gate.

817
00:35:24.480 --> 00:35:26.720
We're just talking about the gates of death

818
00:35:26.720 --> 00:35:27.680
like going out.

819
00:35:28.840 --> 00:35:30.640
Jesus also suffered outside the gate

820
00:35:30.640 --> 00:35:34.080
in order to sanctify the people through his own blood.

821
00:35:35.080 --> 00:35:39.840
Therefore, let us go to him outside the camp

822
00:35:39.840 --> 00:35:42.600
and bear the reproach he endured.

823
00:35:42.600 --> 00:35:45.760
For here we have no lasting city

824
00:35:45.760 --> 00:35:48.200
but we seek the city that is to come.

825
00:35:50.320 --> 00:35:51.040
So what are we to do?

826
00:35:51.040 --> 00:35:53.680
So Jesus suffered outside the gate.

827
00:35:53.680 --> 00:35:55.200
Let me say like we're gonna go,

828
00:35:55.200 --> 00:35:56.080
we want to be with him

829
00:35:56.080 --> 00:35:58.840
even if that means suffering with him.

830
00:35:58.840 --> 00:36:01.000
So what are we then doing?

831
00:36:01.200 --> 00:36:03.520
Says for through him then,

832
00:36:03.520 --> 00:36:08.520
let us continually offer up a sacrifice of praise to God

833
00:36:09.540 --> 00:36:14.540
that is the fruit of lips that acknowledge his name.

834
00:36:14.800 --> 00:36:17.320
So even in the midst of suffering,

835
00:36:17.320 --> 00:36:20.000
as we look to the one who was highly exalted

836
00:36:20.000 --> 00:36:21.600
and yet suffered in our place,

837
00:36:22.640 --> 00:36:27.640
we offer up our sacrifices of praise to him.

838
00:36:28.080 --> 00:36:29.780
So let's pray together, shall we?

839
00:36:31.680 --> 00:36:34.720
Lord, I pray that you would make us a people

840
00:36:34.720 --> 00:36:38.760
