841
00:36:38.760 --> 00:36:41.520
or because you are worthy to be praised,

842
00:36:41.520 --> 00:36:43.800
not only by our lips, but by our lives.

843
00:36:44.840 --> 00:36:46.920
Lord, you do wondrous deeds

844
00:36:46.920 --> 00:36:50.360
