847
00:36:57.720 --> 00:37:00.240
Or we know that even in our suffering,

848
00:37:00.280 --> 00:37:03.680
you reign supreme and our hope is found in you.

849
00:37:03.680 --> 00:37:06.440
Lord, I pray that you would open our hearts

850
00:37:06.440 --> 00:37:09.640
and our mouths that we might sing your praise.

851
00:37:10.840 --> 00:37:12.680
In Jesus' name, amen.

